- ⏳ Criterion 2 (Lint check passes) — DEFERRED to deploy step; requires Dataverse access for Deploy-Playbook.ps1
- ⏳ Criterion 3 (PlaybookExecutionEngine builds N-active-node graph at invocation) — DEFERRED to deploy step
- ⏳ Criterion 4 (Smoke test produces Observations from fixture end-to-end) — DEFERRED to deploy step; 11 unit tests cover the executors + engine patches independently
- ✅ Criterion 5 (Behavior parity with r1 IngestOrchestrator documented + intentional) — parity check documented inline in playbook JSON + ObservationEmitter_ResultShape_MatchesR1InsightsIngestResult test verifies result shape exactly mirrors InsightsIngestResult
- ✅ Criterion 6 (Quality gates pass — code-review + adr-check) — Code Review: 0 critical, 1 warning (ObservationEmitterNodeExecutor 5-param ctor; matches r1 IngestOrchestrator pattern), 2 suggestions. ADR Check: 0 violations, 2 informational warnings (Zone A boundary follows established pattern; deploy coordination per bff-extensions §F.4)
    </completion-summary>

